{"tid":1023291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"二手樓價指數按周漲0.26%　新界區全報升","createTime":"2019-02-15T15:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T16:05:23.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dccc9fccb78f1f3df01205b03942139fbfca3b4c","tid":1023291,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190215/photo/bkn-20190215160237758-0215_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190215181247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190215160237758-0215_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190215181247&h=cd927f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二手交投回升，業主叫價轉強，帶動價格回穩。中原城市領先指數CCL報170.39點，按周上升0.26%。中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報171.35點，按周上升0.29%。CCL(中小型單位)報170.13點，按周升0.40%。CCL(大型單位)報171.70點，按周跌0.43%。<br />\n<br />\n今周新界兩區指數相隔6周後再度齊升，兼且同樣升幅顯著。新界東CCL_Mass報181.21點，按周升2.07%，連升2周共2.81%。新界西CCL_Mass報156.12點，按周升1.08%。近4周計，新界東指數出現3升1跌，有望率先止跌回升。新界西指數亦2升2跌，走勢繼續反覆。港島CCL_Mass報177.08點，按周跌0.29%。九龍CCL_Mass報165.65點，按周跌0.65%。"},{"pid":"33a4143920436743dcfcc667bab5bb2167d052a1","tid":1023291,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"小陽春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}